  "text": "A diploid assembly for AWRI953 (B. anomalus) was also generated. Paired-end reads were mapped to the haploid assembly with BWA-MEM, and high-confidence SNPs were called using VarScan v2.3.9 [CITATION_1] . Nanopore reads were mapped to the assembly using BWA-MEM.",
